name: Melancholy of Doubt and Fear
description:
as the day goes by, as I kept going on. There are always felt doubt and fear.

Wondering if the time can remove those feeling or even is the time that produces those feelings instead?

The time which always haunts you, and makes you doubt yourself, and everything around you. not fixing the feelings, instead of terrorizing and reproducing doubts and fears.

Drowned with the doubts and the fears, as I kept walking, by the time going.
